snippet.title: Media Factory
snippet.description:
We're a community of media makers who work in tv, film, radio, and more. At the MEDIA FACTORY, we provide the tools, training, space and access to distribution that give you the power to share your story.

The MEDIA FACTORY is home to the community, education and government access and WBTV-LP 99.3 FM. Located in the South End Arts District of Burlington, Vermont.

More at https://mediafactory.org
